      "role": "user",
      "content": "wait, why did you call it a goblin? i'm just trying to understand the actual physics of the moment resistance at the support. can you explain the mathematical relationship between the load distance and the moment at the fixed point? I need to be able to write this down in technical terms for my exam.",
